  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.2.1",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.2.1",
  "body": "## Update:\r\n- Synchronized languages from [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- LWJGL: Updated to 3.3.6\r\n- Java Runtime: Added JRE 25\r\n- Updates: Changelogs now use Markdown format\r\n- CurseForge: Added Performance and Other categories\r\n- Patcher: Disabled Create mod warnings on Pojav\r\n- Settings: Added Filipino to the language list\r\n\r\n\r\n## Fix:\r\n- Options:\r\n  - Always disable the \"Narrator\" option\r\n  - Always disable the \"Touchscreen Mode\" option\r\n- Save Management: Unable to read seeds from the new save data structure"
